snippet.title: Trick art dungeon - Game Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Trick art dungeon - Game Announcement Trailer

: Reality and Imagination meets here
A boy lost his way in a museum. He struggles to seek for 
his parents using trick arts Through various trick arts and 
gimmicks, the player can enjoy a beautiful, marvelous 
experience in every moment.
